"Feature name: WLAN
Used to do WLAN test and check WLAN status by RD.
There are 4 test items: Tx, Rx, MCR, NVRAM.
Tx: Test WLAN send packages at different frequencies, rates, power and so on. It needs special instruments to analyze the results.
Rx: Test WLAN receive packages at different frequencies and bandwidth. It will show the results of received packages.
MCR: Read and write WLAN control register. Warning: The operation of non-professionals is forbidden.
NVRAM: Read and write WLAN NVRAM, could accessed in word or byte string.
"
Do not accept packet count = 0, unlimited on Android
